# .cursorignore - Cursor AI Context Protection
# Version: 2.0
# 
# This file prevents sensitive files from being loaded into Cursor's AI context.
# CRITICAL: Cursor loads your entire workspace into Claude's context window.
# Any file NOT ignored here could be exposed to the AI model.
# 
# Place this file in your repository root.
# 
# Documentation: https://docs.cursor.com/context/ignore-files

